  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Leakage of fluid from the subglottic space to the lungs occurs along the longitudinal folds
      within the wall of endotracheal tube (ETT) cuffs. In this project the researchers investigate
      the possible effect of swallowing on the pressure course in the ETT cuff.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
